titleStmt.title: A list of the several reversionary annuities, to which the Million Bank are intituled for the residue of a term of 96 years, to be computed from the 25th. day of January, 1695. to commence after the deceases of the respective nominees, and payable out of the duties of excise and tunnage, setled by act of Parliament.
